\( \displaystyle t + 3 = t^2 + 9 \)?$BR",
"No",
"Is \( x = 4 \) a solution to the equation
\( \displaystyle x + 3 = x^2 - 9 \)?$BR",
"Yes",
"Is \( a = 0 \) a solution to the equation
